project.strategy

Enum Strategy.Name

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Strategy.Name>
      • project.strategy.Strategy.Name
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Strategy.Name>
    Enclosing interface:
    Strategy

    public static enum Strategy.Name
extends java.lang.Enum<Strategy.Name>
    Name enumeration represents different menu choices START represents the menu where we select player types MAINMENU represents main options available for each player where they get their turn CHOOSE_LANTERN_HAND represents options to pick a lantern card from player stack while performing a lantern card exchange CHOOSE_LANTERN_SUPPLY represents options to pick a lantern card from supply stack while performing a lantern card exchange MAKE_DEDICATION represents options to select a dedication a player wants to make SELECT_LAKE represents options while selecting a lake tile to place from a player hand SELECT_BOARD_POSITION represents options to select a position on the board to place a lake tile SELECT_LAKE_ROTATION represents options to select a rotation of the lake tile before placing it on the board
